{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you be ready to tell your sister a lie, because I'm going to separate them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In order to save her life, I have to separate them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember this story as vividly as today, what happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this Unterscharfuhrer Wunsch went over there, took the baby from that woman, and he told her that he's going to give the baby to somebody else to hold for a while.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At first she was-- you know, which mother wants to part from her baby?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she didn't know what really is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But eventually, she stayed alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She saved her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they both, even today, live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a-- a good friend of mine with whom I was in touch for many, many, many years-- and he was one of the guys who-- who I gave access to sleep in my room when I was on this detail from the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Maurice [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He dedicated his life after the war to go to all the German trials, wherever he knew any of the Nazis or the SS by name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He would always go to testify.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was his task.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't-- he had incomes different, and he didn't have to get involved in the daily living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this man, while I was visiting Israel several times, was always telling me on-- on what's going on with these different kinds of trials.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one day, when I came there for a visit, he told me that this Unterscharfuhrer Wunsch sent his wife to Israel to meet her.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She should come to Germany to plead for her husband's life, because he was locked up now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was awaiting a trial for all kinds of whatever they had against him.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
